<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-7055] Broken CQL Version number in 2.0.7</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7055</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Cassandra 2.0.7 has introduced 2 changes in the CQL language:&lt;br/&gt;
*Add uuid() function (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6473&quot; title=&quot;Add CQL function to generate random UUID&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6473&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6473&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
*Add support for DELETE ... IF EXISTS to CQL3 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5708&quot; title=&quot;Add DELETE ... IF EXISTS to CQL3&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5708&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5708&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately the &lt;tt&gt;cql_version&lt;/tt&gt; hasn&apos;t been incremented as reported in the &lt;tt&gt;system.local&lt;/tt&gt; table.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In 2.0.6:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;cqlsh&amp;gt; select cql_version from system.local;

 cql_version
-------------
       3.1.5
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In 2.0.7:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;cqlsh&amp;gt; select cql_version from system.local;

 cql_version
-------------
       3.1.5
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
